<subSubSection id="88A265909DB616FD884AA3EADF7B55B9" pageId="1" pageNumber="32" type="latin">
<paragraph id="B5F2EF2FB0BE2F454D4AF024D70C0255" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">
<emphasis id="2D45D379AD4EF28448D131665801589A" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">Resembling</emphasis>
Rhodamnia latifolia 
<emphasis id="D78D23382792F7A3E3CD6F56C6AE7192" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="32">but with distinctly larger leaves that have an acute to acuminate apex and differing by the larger fruits</emphasis>
